    <div class="mt-16 max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">The last 2 years have been a struggle.</h2>
      <p class="mt-6">Not really caring about any company I got a job at, I havent lasted long ant any of them. For the last 2 years I held 3 jobs. One for 7 months. 
      Another for 6, and the last one was a contract that only lasted a month. Not from bad performance, but from taking too long to do things.</p>
      <p class="mt-8">It's been a real challenge, putting in hours toward someone else's "get rich" plan when all you want to do is work on something that feels 
      important for the future of humanity.</p>
      <p class="mt-8">When your motivations lie in making sure your great grand children, who you'll never meet, live in a world that is good. 
      Everything else is difficult to work on.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">You're probably thinking I'm irresponsible</h2>
      <p class="mt-6">Its taken being responsible to work for people. But my girlfriend actually convinced me that I need to stop hiding my talents from the world. I promised her that I would. So here I am. Comitted to keeping my promise and making something that might be useful to humanity.</p>
       <figure class="mt-10 border-l border-indigo-600 pl-9">
        <blockquote class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
          <p> So no more time and energy is wasted helping someone else fulfill their dreams.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </figure>
      
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">So I decided to say "Fuck It."</h2>
      <p class="mt-6">I'm an artist. The energy that I've spent working the 9 to 5 has been a soul suicide. I've been sitting on this art ever 
      since I lived in El Salvador. I barley knew the language and didn't know anyone when I moved there so I spent my alone time at night making 
      these pieces. Each one has it's own story you can see in their descriptions.</p>
      <p class="mt-6">This is my full time job now</p>
      <p class="mt-6">Selling art.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">And I still want to help humanity.</h2>
      <p class="mt-6">So that's why I'm selling these NFT's. You're not buying the NFT, your buying the physical art. the NFT just gives you some unique features. <%= link_to "How it works", how_it_works_path, class: "font-semibold text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500" %> </p>
      <p class="mt-6">This seems like a good way to bring crypto into the physical world. There are a lot of things possible but I'm starting off small. As a humble artist and a failed developer. Maybe this can be useful to the world</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">This won't be just for me.</h2>
      <p class="mt-6">Right now I'm the only one selling art here. I'm doing that on purpose. This is a new realm for everyone. There are many unknowns.</p>
      <p class="mt-6">Once I've sold enough of this collection, and tested the protocol in the real world, this website will be open for anyone to add their art. This will help artists and buyers of fine art, and ensure quality NFT's are made. Not randomly generated JPEGS. </p>
      <p class="mt-6"><%= link_to "See The Roadmap", timeline_path, class: "font-semibold text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500" %>  </p>
    </div>
